    {
      "id": "18d4750c-f3ba-8086-964b-c8b836c87b85",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Bayesian Knowledge Tracing is popular method in Intelligent-Tutoring Systems that uses skill-specific parameters, but often fails to account for student variability. Thus, the authors propose an improvement to BKT which hinges on the introduction of student-specifc parameters. ",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "18d4750c-f3ba-8086-964b-c8b836c87b85",
        "parent": {
