    {
      "id": "18d4750c-f3ba-8002-a7a2-d76de5b524b7",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Results show that the introduction of these parameters greatly improves the prediction capabilities of BKT on new students. In addition, they also show that parameterizing speed of learning also beats parameterizing a-priori knowledge.",
